{"type":"article","id":4866,"title":"为什么Cultural Marxism甚至Jewish Bolshevism的阴谋论能在中国经过包装后进入粉红思想","uid":13059,"topics":[731],"contents":"关于这个阴谋论的定义：<br>\nhttps://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Cultural_Marxism<br>\nThe term alludes to a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Conspiracy_theory\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">conspiracy theory</a>&nbsp;in which sinister left-wingers have infiltrated&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Liberal_media\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">media</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Liberal_academia\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">academia</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Evil_Liberal_Science_Conspiracy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">science</a>&nbsp;and are engaged in a decades-long plot to undermine&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Western_culture\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Western culture</a>. Some variants of the conspiracy&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Jonanism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">allege that basically all of modern social liberalism is</a>, in fact, a Communist&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Front_group\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">front group</a>.<br>\n<br>\n而粉红的言论中不乏这样的理念：<br>\nThe term alludes to a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Conspiracy_theory\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">conspiracy theory</a>&nbsp;in which sinister Americans have infiltrated&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Liberal_media\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">media</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Liberal_academia\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">academia</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Evil_Liberal_Science_Conspiracy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">science</a>&nbsp;and are engaged in a decades-long plot to undermine Eastern<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Western_culture\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">&nbsp;culture</a>. Some variants of the conspiracy&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Jonanism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">allege that basically all of modern social liberalism is</a>, in fact, an American&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rationalwiki.org/wiki/Front_group\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">front group</a>.","date":"2019-09-10","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}